Package: llmshieldr
Title: Safety Guardrails for LLM Workflows in R
Version: 0.2.0
Description: A provider-agnostic safety layer for R developers building with
    large language models. Covers all ten OWASP LLM Top 10 (2025) risk
    categories via a composable rule engine. Supports rule-based and semantic
    (LLM-reviewer) checks on prompts, retrieved context, and model outputs.
    Works with any R-callable LLM provider. Suitable for all industries.
